    //   threshold = base x staminaScale / sqrt(playerDrain)
    // where staminaScale is the engine's own per-ball fatigue curve inverted
    // (1.35/(1.85-st/100) bowling, 1.25/(1.75-st/100) batting; exactly 1.0 at
